{
  "stem": "19690.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 55.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "We had Shabbat dinner together in a restaurant and then went to services and then we stayed at our hotel-- my father, my mother, and I-- the same as the other visitors.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "So we were together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "On Saturday morning-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] --we went to services-- [PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] --and it probably was the most [SOBBING] important day of my life.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS] [CRYING] My father had the same day of his bar mitzvah and I sang the same Torah portion as he had sung just before.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] --he stood behind me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "[SOBBING] I could feel the pride that he had in what was going on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "That afternoon, we had lunch at the hotel with everybody and a discussion started about what was happening.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "There was rumors around that things were changing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And my father's friend said, I'm going into hiding immediately after I leave here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "I want you, meaning my father, to come with him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And since we had contacts in Switzerland, which is how my grandparents communicated with us from Germany-- these people were friends of Ruth and [INAUDIBLE] mother and father, who was in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These friends were friends of hers who had become our contact.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everything-- everyone knew if something happens to anybody, this is who you write to.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he said-- so this friend of my father's said, you have these friends.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Go there.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Get out now.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They wouldn't hear of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The weekend was very pleasant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Everybody left, my father went back to camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And by the way, I might add that in that time, he had been moved to a labor camp called Miramar, which is also in the same area of the Provence.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
